OL,3,CFirst black female CoE deacon loses
OL,4,Cappeal over decision to dissolve parish
OL,6,FIn February, Rev Clarke and her parish
OL,7,Fof All Saints Spring Park brought an
OL,8,Fappeal to the Judicial Committee of
OL,9,Fthe Privy Council, with justices told
OL,10,Fthe abolition of the parish would have
OL,11,Fa "disproportionate impact" on BAME
OL,12,F(black, Asian and minority ethnic)
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,FBut in a judgment on Tuesday, justices
OL,16,Fat the court ` which hears appeals
OL,17,Ffrom several Commonwealth countries as
OL,18,Fwell as on some ecclesiastical issues
OL,19,F` dismissed the appeals.
