OL,6,FFollowing the ruling, a spokesperson
OL,7,Ffor the CoE's commissioners said: "The
OL,8,Fchurch commissioners note this
OL,9,Fjudgment and welcome the fact that the
OL,10,Fcourt described the case made by the
OL,11,Fcommissioners' statement of reasons as
OL,12,F'compelling'.
OL,14,F"The court also confirmed that it was
OL,15,Fsatisfied that the decision to make
OL,16,Fthe scheme did not involve unlawful
OL,17,Fdiscrimination and that the
OL,18,Fcommissioners had not failed to
OL,19,Fconsider the impact of the proposals
OL,20,Fon the UK minority ethnic community in
OL,21,FShirley."
